OL,3,CConsumers set to get compensation for
OL,4,Cfaulty smart meters and install delays
OL,6,FHouseholds will be able to get
OL,7,Fcompensation from suppliers for delays
OL,8,Fto smart meter installation, the
OL,9,Fenergy watchdog has said.
OL,11,FOfgem has unveiled proposals to bring
OL,12,Fin rules that will see consumers
OL,13,Feligible for #40 compensation if they
OL,14,Fhave to wait more than six weeks for a
OL,15,Fsmart meter installation.
OL,17,FIt will also include faulty meters and
OL,18,Fthose not operating in smart mode
OL,19,Fwhich are not fixed within 90 days.
