OL,6,FMr Lewis said: "Far too many smart
OL,7,Fmeters, likely one in five, don't work
OL,8,Fas they should ` a problem not just
OL,9,Ffor all the homes with broken ones,
OL,10,Fbut for the smart meter rollout.
OL,12,F"With so many dissatisfied customers,
OL,13,Fword-of-mouth is bad, so people tell
OL,14,Ftheir friends and neighbours not to
OL,15,Fget one.
