OL,4,Cfaulty smart meters and install delays
OL,6,F"We need to shift firms' focus from
OL,7,Fjust installing smart meters to
OL,8,Fpromptly fixing those that are broken
OL,9,F` not just meters that go into dumb
OL,10,Fmode, but crucially all elements,
OL,11,Fincluding in-home displays that stop
OL,12,Fworking."
OL,14,FOfgem said that by extending rules to
OL,15,Fcover poor connectivity, it will mean
OL,16,Fmore consumers can get compensation.
