OL,3,CConsumers set to get compensation for
OL,4,Cfaulty smart meters and install delays
OL,6,FCharlotte Friel, director of retail
OL,7,Fpricing and systems at Ofgem, said:
OL,8,F"Millions of consumers rely on their
OL,9,Fsmart meter every day for accurate
OL,10,Fbilling, cheaper tariffs, automatic
OL,11,Fmeter readings and real-time data to
OL,12,Fhelp keep track of spending.
OL,14,F"But we know many customers that want
OL,15,Fa smart meter wait too long to get one
OL,16,Finstalled or face delays on repairs
OL,17,Fwhen it stops working ` this needs to
OL,18,Fchange."
