OL,11,FShe added: "These new rules are about
OL,12,Fsetting clear expectations of
OL,13,Fsuppliers, incentivising them to boost
OL,14,Fsmart meter standards, and protecting
OL,15,Fconsumers from poor service if things
OL,16,Fgo wrong."
OL,18,FThe plans mean that suppliers will
OL,19,Fneed to improve smart meter standards
OL,20,For pay out from early 2026, according
OL,21,Fto Ofgem.
