OL,6,FUnder the new rules, micro-businesses
OL,7,Fwill also be able to get compensation
OL,8,Ffor smart meter issues.
OL,10,FMinister for energy consumers Miatta
OL,11,FFahnbulleh said: "Consumers are at the
OL,12,Fheart of our mission to deliver an
OL,13,Fenergy retail market that works for
OL,14,Feveryone, as we accelerate towards a
OL,15,Fclean, homegrown power system to
OL,16,Fprotect households against global
OL,17,Ffossil fuel price spikes.
